metadata.name: Boketto #5
metadata.description:
'Boketto' is the act of gazing vacantly into the distance without a thought.

On the process of making this collection, i explored interfering patterns in order to give an abstract and more painted look on the canvas.

--Features--

Palette : 14 different color palettes
Scheme : 11 different schemes
Step : 7 different steps
Rotation : 9 types (each type has more than 30 different outcomes)

Press "s" to save a 1600x2000 PNG

High resolution outputs will be uploaded on my (under contruction) site soon 

Made with p5js & ‚ù§Ô∏è

Gtsiliakos_art, October 2022

metadata.name: GEN XYZ Das Occult #2165
metadata.description:
A 10k Generative Profile Pic collection
GEN XYZ Das Occult - by culla - @tamccullough

move over cryptopunks
there is a new group on the scene

100% code - not an image composition

A bunch of common palettes
A selection of rare palettes
And a smaller set of ultra rare palettes
However, rarity will be based on what combinations the code produces

The majority of tokens will not have a special trait
However your token might have one or even multiple special traits
But, be aware that only the last special trait added will be listed in the features

Even then, look closely, because not all aspects of the canvas are included in the features. Collectors should still look closely and choose what they like when buying on secondary.

Which team are you on? X or O?

follow culla on twitter for updates. Or maybe __acolyte__

Thank you for supporting an emerging artist in the generative art space

2x for each Basqunk held
1x for each Inkspunk, TwoFourQunk, V0iD, DeeManz, Punkasso and CR0$$KULL
You would have needed to transfer the above tokens to your mint wallet at the time of the snapshot

share your tokens on social media with #genxyznft
Made with love by culla using p5.js

metadata.name: SINGULARITY #98
metadata.description:
A random generated gravitational singularity travels through the void.
Objects behave in several ways. Many have satellites, some even have two.

Each singularity occurs in different space.
Some are colorful, some are minimal. 
Beware of the solar winds. They can mess things.
A tiny part of singularity will end up in a solar storm.

Good luck!

Coded in Amsterdam with Javascript & Hydra.
twitter.com/dnlsmms
instagr.am/dnlsmm.studio

metadata.name: Calligraphic #11
metadata.description: CALLIGRAPHIC is an exploration of a layered writing system where multicolored strokes are overlaid on top of each other to express new meanings. Each minted artwork's unique positioning, stroke combinations and coloring is determined by a random seed hash.

metadata.name: Sleepless #57
metadata.description:
Sleepless is a generative art project made from p5.js. Inspired by the artist's travels, the project emulates a window view of a distant city at night. Variations include randomization of different window elements (frames and bars) and city elements (buildings, planes and ships). It is also mintable in several foreground and background colors. The colors and dithering were selected to create a charcoal texture.

Press 'S' to download a high res PNG.
Due to the preview image being compressed to fit your window size, the dithering may look different from the high res PNG.

NFTs minted are under the NFT License 2.0 (https://www.nftlicense.org/)

This piece allows you to scan the QR code to see the hash that has created it. Every piece is unique.
